    "Name": "Decurion APC",
    "Details": "An upgraded model of the Decurion APC, the Decurion APC MK.II entered service in 3061. Created with assistance from the Word of Blake, the project engineers took inspiration from the Decurion MK.II. The Decurion APC's 125-rated ICE was swapped for a 170-rated Fusion Core and the armor boosted to 10 tons. Retaining the 5 ton infantry bay, the engineers added a Medium Pulse Laser to the turret and a pair of Machine Guns were added to the front of the APC.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Biome Restrictions: None.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 8/12 hexes / 240/360 meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Armor\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       170     25\n<b>Left</b>         145     25\n<b>Right</b>       145     25\n<b>Rear</b>        145     25\n<b>Turret</b>      170     25\n\n<b>Total</b>      775    125</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Improved Targeting - Short</color>\n\n<color=#ffcc00> Can carry 1 Battle Armor Squads.</color>",
